title.rendered: Basement Ground Triplex For Sale In Vasant Vihar

content.rendered:
Prepared to be impressed when you enter this superbly maintained basement ground triplex set on a sprawling 400sq yds occupying a peaceful wide street position facing north-west side. this home enjoys abundant natural light and a layout designed for easy living and entertaining. The ground floor incorporates a generously proportioned kitchen with tasteful interiors, fully functional appliances, a welcoming living and dining room, and a guest powder room. you will find four dreamy bedrooms with attached bathrooms. The master bedroom ensuite bathroom and adjoining balcony encourage relaxation. other highlights of this property include a separate driveway, automatic lift, three spacious car parking spaces, and a cute set of plants that will welcome you at the entrance.
Vasant Vihar is developed as a posh residential colony with each block having its own market and park. you’ll find many embassies in Vasant Vihar including the United States, Argentina, Romania, etc. the colony is very green and clean and has several prestigious educational institutes in close proximity. The Indira Gandhi International Airport is just 10km away from this location.
